      "y": 1225,
      "width": 700,
      "height": 150,
      "text": "KV Store \u2192 Cosmos DB (NoSQL)          |  Vector Index \u2192 Azure AI Search (Vector)\nBM25 Search \u2192 Azure AI Search (BM25)  |  Graph \u2192 Cosmos DB (Adjacency Lists)\nHooks/Events \u2192 Azure Event Hubs       |  Workers \u2192 Azure Functions\nSingle Runtime \u2192 Container Apps        |  Local Disk \u2192 Azure Blob Storage\nNo Auth \u2192 Entra ID + API Management   |  LLM Providers \u2192 Azure OpenAI",
